Package: freedict-editor
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: yelp, xbase-clients, gv
Suggests: tei
Description: Editor for Text Encoding Initiative XML dictionaries
 Entries are made from a subset of the format defined by TEI, Version 4,
 Chapter 12 "Print Dictionaries".  Supports
  * online validation
  * XPath to flexibly select entries to be edited
  * easy, user friendly Form View to edit entries
  * fallback to plain XML editing
  * entering pronunciation in IPA characters
  * HTML preview of formatted entries
  * sanity checks and a spell checker
 .
 TEI XML is used in the FreeDict project to store bilingual dictionary data.
